   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Greetings to Horion.  Send to me tomorrow, which is the [l. 5] fourteenth, a tasty fish.  For you know [l. 10] that it is my official birthday. Farewell. The 13th.</ab>
